==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Squaw man
<hw>Squaw man</hw>. <def>A white man who has married an Indian squaw;
sometimes, one who has gained tribal rights by such a marriage; -- often
a term of contempt.</def> <mark>[Western U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Squawroot</ent>⟦br⟧
